About Me

A creative individual with an engineer's mindset and a passion for bringing ideas to life.

I am a creative individual with an engineer's mindset and a passion for bringing ideas to life. Skilled in machine operating, machine maintenance, strategic planning, circuit board design, rapid prototyping, electronics testing, 3D print design, and product manufacturing. For the last few years of experience managing my own company Adventure Audio, where I have gained expertise in management, sales, distribution, customer relationships, retail partnerships, payroll accounting, brand marketing, and supply chain management. Proven ability to work independently and as part of a team, with a strong work ethic and a desire to contribute my skills and experience to a challenging and rewarding farm work environment. Proven green thumb with experience growing a variety of vegetables in personal gardens.
